                <h1>How Long Does a First Advantage Background Check Take?</h1>
                <p>The duration of a First Advantage background check typically ranges from a few days to a couple of weeks. Several factors influence this timeline, including the type of check requested, the completeness of the applicant's provided information, and the responsiveness of third-party verification sources. Patience is key!</p>
